Njikoka bụ ọchịchị ime obodo na steeti Anambra, ndịda-ọwụwa anyanwụ Nigeria
Towns that make up the local government include Abagana, Enugwu-Agidi, Enugwu-ukwu, Nawfia, Nimo, Abba town, and Umuriam-Nawfia.
Nke a bu uloakwukwo ndi di na Mpaghara Njikoka Lokal Goomenti Aria:
